<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.6.4">
<l>viṇṭārai veṉṟāvi vilaṅkuṇṇa melliyalār</l>
<l>koṇṭāṭum mallakala maḻalēṟa veñcamattuk</l>
<l>kaṇṭāraik kaṭalmallait talacayaṉat tuṟaivārai</l>
<l>koṇṭāṭum neñcuṭaiyā ravareṅkaḷ kulateyvamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those with hearts that celebrate him who appeared</l>
<l rend="indent">on the burning battlefield</l>
<l>When fire rose from the proud chest that was celebrated by delicate [ladies],</l>
<l>Having conquered the enemies so that animals consumed their lives,</l>
<l>Him who dwells in Talacayaṉam at Mallai by the sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">they are our family deities.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
